{"tid":1285862,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"正式宣布：革 命 完 畢 - 曲 終 人 散 - 告一段落","createTime":"2019-07-04T17:04:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T13:47:53.000Z","uid":209282,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c61a5a556569dd59f161bb900ae10ecface7490d","tid":1285862,"uid":209282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:04:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">告你老味</span><br />\n<br />\n距離立法會選舉仲有少少時間，你地每一個人有<strong>義務同責任</strong>去投票！ <br />\n<br />\n希望各位可以睇住自己屋企既長輩，香港老人家其實為數唔少人，明白佢地未必鍾意年青議員或者泛民，加上老人家落出街成日比建制既街坊宣傳，佢地未必真係鍾意建制，但聽過建制班人個名都可能到時無咩心水，投左個自己聽過既名就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（真人真事）<br />\n<br />\n希望你地可以用返建制既招數，洗返老人家個腦，不斷重覆又重覆建制係衰人，果頭派蛇齋，轉頭減老人福利。<br />\n班老人家就算唔投泛民，甚至投白票都好，要教導佢投建制=扣自己老人津貼。<br />\n<br />\n見到屋企任何建制單傳，出門口掟出面垃圾桶，掉走建制送既揮春月歷等等。<br />\n<br />\n為左打擊掌心雷，如果有長者住老人院，千祈要係投票當日，一早探佢，帶佢地出黎散步飲茶再投票，唔好比佢地跟左老人院去投票，會折壽。<br />\n<br />\n係街見到老人家排哂隊，唔識都好，係佢地身邊佛經式講建制以外號碼，務求等老人家聽到亂哂龍，廢票好過投建制。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a72d17dccd6a18dcf86ab873e926af5dc32a8365","tid":1285862,"uid":209282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:05:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f071d8710e82e698830449a5995064a636dbe280","tid":1285862,"uid":209282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:10:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cb10206fbbc349d1e8aa144d38dcd41e93881f3","tid":1285862,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:11:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"323adbd3f139e636c0ae1f216a8f24d17dfd58c9","tid":1285862,"uid":209282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:12:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb30daa4d57f11394148ef434759a697b251ef2","tid":1285862,"uid":209282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:25:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"238662da6c5be865025fa602ca357a4219da9d06","tid":1285862,"uid":209282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T23:26:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1172361ef5acc7a315b5ba494a5d9ebf48517703","tid":1285862,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T00:54:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63c3f64dba39e84fc7b26a34210ce789c633bb8d","tid":1285862,"uid":209282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:28:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"